name: Rain AI 7 Inverse Higher Rez
description: This is a higher resolution version of "Rain AI 7 Inverse." Except for one of those that had gone to a collector, I burned the remaining 15 and am re-minting 15. Gifting the collector the new, higher rez version. To create this image, I reversed the high resolution digital photo of my acrylic painting "Rain". Then I ran that through an AI filter. It has a completely different spirit, of playfulness and joy, which I really love. The original painting was of downtown LA at night, dark, surreal, about a sad period in my life. Rain represented my tears. Wonderful to have joy emerge from sadness.
